"is <systemitem>/etc/mateconf/<replaceable>mateconf-version-number</replaceable>/"
"path</systemitem>. Each user has a path file. The path file specifies the "
"following information for each configuration source:"
msgstr ""
"Die <application>MateConf</application>-Datenbank enthält eine Reihe von "
